text: Tōgō Heihachirō (Japanese:東郷 平八郎, 27 January 1848 – 30 May 1934) was an admiral of the fleet in the Imperial Japanese Navy, he is well-known as one of the Japanese Navy Heroes. == References == Category:1848 births Category:1934 deaths Category:Recipients of the Order of the Rising Sun
title: Tōgō Heihachirō
